          "type": "default"
        },
        {
          "content": "### 📣 Stripe Payment Notice\n\n**Official Rate:** 0.85 RMB = 1 API Credit. \nWhen paying via Stripe, you may notice a slight difference between the website's estimated price and the final checkout amount.\n\n**Why?** \n\nStripe strictly requires unit prices in integer USD cents. To comply with this rule, we have set our 0.85 RMB rate (approx. $0.116 USD) to **$0.12 USD** in Stripe.\n\nFor example, 10 Credits via Stripe totals **$1.20 USD** (approx. 8.70 RMB). ",
